casebody.data:
The State of Ohio, Appellant, v. Wilburn, Appellee.

[Cite as State v. Wilburn, 104 Ohio St.3d 263, 2004-Ohio-6404.]

(No. 2004-0184 Submitted October 13, 2004 Decided December 8, 2004.) William D. Mason, Cuyahoga County Prosecuting Attorney, and Lisa Reitz Williamson, Assistant Prosecuting Attorney, for appellant. Joseph V. Pagano, for appellee.

{¶ 1} The judgment of the court of appeals is reversed and the cause is remanded to the trial court for resentencing consistent with State v. Jordan, 104 Ohio St.3d 21, 2004-Ohio-6085, 817 N.E.2d 864.

Moyer, C.J., Resnick, F.E. Sweeney, Pfeifer, Lundberg Stratton, O’Connor and O’Donnell, JJ., concur.
